---
title: Breezy Beef Stroganoff with Buttered Cauliflower Rice
description: You'll never want to hunker down in the kitchen again after making this simplified version of the classic. We've done away with the starch-heavy noodles and have re-invented this one with buttered cauliflower rice. You'll never look back!

